Module Math::BigSimple 1.1 Installation Guide.
----------------------------------------------
1.Requrements.
 This module requires Math::BigInt module.
 It should work on pure-perl systems.
2.How to install
 Type the following into your command line:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

 ...and the module is instaled.
 If there are any problems, simply copy the
 lib/Math/BigSimple.pm file to the Math
 subdirectory of your perl modules folder.
